Class RegionController

  • java.lang.Object
    • RegionController

  • public class RegionController
extends java.lang.Object
    Project #4 CS 2334, Section 10 April 22, 2014 The Controller for the graphical user interface. Receives events from the input view (SelectionView) and updates the model's (RegionModel) data.
